(1365, 1, '2018-05-04 06:52:20', '2018-05-04 06:52:20', '[vc_row fullwidth="yes" el_id="home"][vc_column][rev_slider_vc alias="homelight"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1525357233574{background-image: url(http://localhost/nushutter/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/Nu-Shutter-26-1-3.jpg?id=1375) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}" el_id="aboutid" el_class="aboutcls"][vc_column][heading text="About Us" tag="h1" align="center" color="#ef4836"][line_solid icon="circle"][vc_row_inner el_id="aboutsid" el_class="aboutscls"][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_column_text el_id="abtusid" el_class="abtuscls"]NuSpace (earlier called Nushutter) was established in October of 2005 with the intention of creating stellar interior designs. One of our core ideologies is at NuSpace we combine, design, functionality and cutting-edge technology to give homeowners a stress-free home designing process by which they can make their home cosy, comfortable and stylish.\r\n\r\nThe journey started as the fixed furniture market is plagued by an unorganized structure of carpenters. You know what that means, unexplained costs, no post-sales service delays and quality issues. Furthermore, we saw that having conventional interiors leads to regular maintenance work.\r\n\r\nAs a solution, we stepped into the modular market, with the aim to reduce the maintenance and improvise the quality of design. We teamed up with NuPlus, a Pune based company to design stellar kitchens.\r\n<a class="btn-slider" href="#">Read More</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_single_image image="1370" img_size="full" css_animation="zoomIn"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1525360657901{background-image: url(http://localhost/nushutter/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/tv-unit-1.jpg?id=1392) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-